⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Question 91/120 – Data Validation

🎤 Interview Question

Validate an employee dataset using the following rules:

Salary must be greater than 0.

Department cannot be NULL.

Email cannot be NULL.


Return only valid records.


---

📊 Input Dataset

emp_id	salary	department	email

101	60000	IT	a@test.com
102	-1000	HR	b@test.com
103	50000	NULL	c@test.com
104	45000	Finance	NULL



---

✅ Expected Output

emp_id

101



---

✅ Recommended Solution

from pyspark.sql.functions import col

valid_df = (
    df.filter(col("salary") > 0)
      .filter(col("department").isNotNull())
      .filter(col("email").isNotNull())
)


---

